# Healthcare Services Common Library

## Package Structure
```
org.btsn.healthcare.common/
├── base/
│   ├── BaseHealthcareService.java          # Abstract base class
│   ├── ServiceAssessment.java              # Base assessment interface
│   └── TokenInfo.java                      # Common token data structure
├── json/
│   ├── JsonResponseBuilder.java            # Fluent JSON builder
│   ├── JsonTokenParser.java               # Token parsing utilities
│   └── JsonValidator.java                 # JSON validation utilities
├── exceptions/
│   ├── ServiceProcessingException.java    # Custom service exceptions
│   └── JsonParsingException.java          # JSON-specific exceptions
└── utils/
    ├── SequenceUtils.java                 # ID generation utilities
    ├── DatabaseUtils.java                 # Common database operations
    └── TimestampUtils.java               # Time formatting utilities
```

## Maven/Gradle Dependency
```xml
<dependency>
    <groupId>org.btsn.healthcare</groupId>
    <artifactId>healthcare-services-common</artifactId>
    <version>1.0.0</version>
</dependency>
```